{"tid":2291954,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：料明年首季平均加薪0.8%　數碼轉型相關工種加薪最高","createTime":"2020-11-19T06:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:22:28.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d138dd49d5f5dd1bb0ff532c992061f35fab1c13","tid":2291954,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"有調查預計香港明年首季打工仔平均加薪0.8%，屬近10年最低加幅；整體有63%僱主傾向在明年首季凍結或維持現有人手。<br />\n<br />\nJobsDB於今年9月就2021年首季的招聘、薪酬及福利意向進行調查，今日公布最新《招聘、薪酬及福利調查報告》。該調查預計明年首季打工仔平均加薪0.8%，屬近10年最低加幅。此幅度較 2019 年調查預期的 +2.7% 進一步下調近 2個百分點，而加薪幅度相對較大的工種包括數據分析（+3.8%）、營銷及業務拓展（+2.4%）及教育（+2.1%）等。<br />\n<br />\n花紅及福利方面，逾7成僱主（72%）表示於2020年有發放花紅及雙糧，較去年下降 12個百分點，而花紅平均為 1.4 個月，與去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2805969/jobs2021_op_Master_Output11180949_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2805969%2Fjobs2021_op_Master_Output11180949_1024.jpg&h=9ea980b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7%企業有意削減人手<br />\n<br />\n疫情反覆，不少企業對經濟前景均抱持審慎態度。2021年首季方面，料 63% 企業會凍結人手，較去年的35%上升28個百分點。更有7%表示會削減人手以減低營運成本，當中以前線及基層職員（78%）最受影響。<br />\n<br />\n展望來年發展，64%企業期望市況能於 2021 年內回復至疫情前水平，保守估計第二季（19%）及第三季（20%）陸續復甦的佔其中大多數。人手規模較大的企業預期較早恢復招聘計劃，當中50% 認為可於2021年上半年復原，中小企招聘方面則相對審慎。<br />\n<br />\n市場需求較大的6個工種則包括銷售及業務拓展（24%）、會計（18%）、行政及人力資源（12%）、金融（12%）、採購及買辦（12%）和零售及銷售（12%）。<br />\n<br />\n企業於疫情下在招聘態度亦有顯著改變，報告指出有７成僱主認為求職者的相關經驗依然是最重要的考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2805969/jobs2021_op_Point02C_Output1118_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2805969%2Fjobs2021_op_Point02C_Output1118_1024.jpg&h=2108d7a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c260028a335d6d2f2d7beb00cca41e1d4240661d","tid":2291954,"uid":29153,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"又話經濟差，仲有人工加？"},{"pid":"78ab258c3ae0efd1f0ce0a25fd989bbb7a86a240","tid":2291954,"uid":225192,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c260028a335d6d2f2d7beb00cca41e1d4240661d","tid":2291954,"uid":29153,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"又話經濟差，仲有人工加？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"班賤民有冇得加唔知<br />\n鳩吹定方便政府加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a900cf6e04131c4dc4141df6e1c337e13917b0b2","tid":2291954,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 加得仲低過定存<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f61c88c06605eb864c40d2fd100cc19ba6e1951","tid":2291954,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c260028a335d6d2f2d7beb00cca41e1d4240661d","tid":2291954,"uid":29153,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"又話經濟差，仲有人工加？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"你唔要比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a3b49dde43cbb469fa2dea9eb3fb53aea4b62d","tid":2291954,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"港企就算唔夠人都可以繼續cut<br />\n<br />\n中資就靠阿爺條水喉射住<br />\nR到腳趾就黎爛都可以繼續請人"},{"pid":"449098b1bcffd8e0da8692251d94bb77a15e57ea","tid":2291954,"uid":98899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"壓價文  差你老母咩  幾個行業死姐"},{"pid":"4c7d5efb01824ae62fe82a9d6a14c965f8589f73","tid":2291954,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aefae3a152eb50994a7b5c6dc6c44ac2840623","tid":2291954,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d138dd49d5f5dd1bb0ff532c992061f35fab1c13","tid":2291954,"uid":66271,"like":0,"disl